<odoo>
  <record id="ir_ui_view_4048" model="ir.ui.view">
    <field name="arch" type="xml">
      <xpath expr="//div[hasclass('oe_empty')]" position="replace">
          <div class="oe_structure oe_empty" t-att-data-editor-message="editor_message">
            <section class="s_text_block pt40 pb40 o_colored_level" data-snippet="s_text_block" data-name="Text">
              <div class="container s_allow_columns">
                <p>Step into the world of winemaking with our <strong>immersive winery tour</strong>, where tradition meets innovation. Stroll among the vines that give life to our finest blends, breathe in the aromas of ripening grapes, and learn the secrets behind each harvest.</p>
                <p>In our <strong>cellar</strong>, you’ll explore rows of oak barrels quietly shaping the character of our wines. From fermentation tanks to blending rooms, you’ll see every step of the journey — from grape to glass.</p>
                <p>Your visit ends with a <strong>guided tasting</strong> of our signature creations, including the bold <strong>Bordoo Grand Cru</strong>, the vibrant <strong>Odoomatic Spice</strong>, and the elegant <strong>Pinodoo Noir</strong>. Each sip tells a story of passion, craftsmanship, and the unique terroir that defines our vineyard.</p>
                <p>Whether you’re a wine enthusiast or simply curious, our tour is a feast for the senses — and a memory to savor.</p>
                <p><strong>Includes:</strong> Vineyard walk, cellar visit, guided tasting of 3 wines</p>
                <p><strong>Languages:</strong> EN / CH / FR</p>
              </div>
            </section>
            <section class="s_image_gallery o_spc-small o_masonry pt24 pb24 o_colored_level" data-vcss="002" data-columns="3" style="overflow: hidden;" data-snippet="s_images_wall" data-name="Images Wall">
              <div class="container">
                <div class="row s_nb_column_fixed">
                  <div class="o_masonry_col o_snippet_not_selectable col-lg-4">
                    <img class="img img-fluid d-block rounded" src="/web/image/vineyard.ir_attachment_18" data-index="0" data-name="Image" alt="" loading="lazy" data-mimetype="image/jpeg"/>
                    <img src="/web/image/vineyard.ir_attachment_1" alt="" data-attachment-id="1139" class="img img-fluid d-block rounded o_we_custom_image" data-format-mimetype="image/webp" data-original-id="1139" data-original-src="/web/image/1139-d3f35704/mauro-lima-VQRmSYDTDjs-unsplash.jpg" data-mimetype-before-conversion="image/jpeg" data-resize-width="690" data-mimetype="image/webp" loading="lazy"/>
                  </div>
                  <div class="o_masonry_col o_snippet_not_selectable col-lg-4">
                    <img class="img img-fluid d-block rounded" src="/web/image/vineyard.ir_attachment_16" data-index="1" data-name="Image" alt="" loading="lazy" data-mimetype="image/jpeg"/>
                    <img src="/web/image/vineyard.ir_attachment_3" alt="" data-attachment-id="1141" class="img img-fluid d-block rounded o_we_custom_image" data-format-mimetype="image/webp" data-original-id="1141" data-original-src="/web/image/1141-fbc09580/jennifer-yung-uSF8kGIeDMw-unsplash.jpg" data-mimetype-before-conversion="image/jpeg" data-resize-width="690" data-mimetype="image/webp" loading="lazy"/>
                  </div>
                  <div class="o_masonry_col o_snippet_not_selectable col-lg-4">
                    <img class="img img-fluid d-block rounded" src="/web/image/vineyard.ir_attachment_15" data-index="2" data-name="Image" alt="" loading="lazy" data-mimetype="image/jpeg"/>
                    <img src="/web/image/vineyard.ir_attachment_2" alt="" data-attachment-id="1140" class="img img-fluid d-block rounded o_we_custom_image" data-format-mimetype="image/webp" data-original-id="1140" data-original-src="/web/image/1140-0b950992/chelsea-pridham-Pj1JHHRqD3c-unsplash.jpg" data-mimetype-before-conversion="image/jpeg" data-resize-width="690" data-mimetype="image/webp" loading="lazy"/>
